We believe we offer a simple, elegant solution to the mire that is modern litigation.  It comes down to this:

  Lawsuits are determined on the issues.
  Issues are decided by the facts.
  Facts are proved with the evidence.
  Evidence comprises people, documents and things.
  
We hope to prove the merits of this simple approach to you, and look forward to your comments about eCaseBase.  

